videoSnippet.title: Smooth Game by Carlsen against Rustam Kasimdzhanov | World Rapid Championship | Round 5
videoSnippet.description:

The "King Salman World Blitz & Rapid Championships 2017" in Riyadh from Decemer 26th to 30th. The first five rounds of the rapid tournament take place on December 26th. A record $2 million prize fund has attracted most of the world's best players.

Magnus Carlsen vs Rustam Kasimdzhanov
World Rapid Championship (2017), Riyadh KSA, rd 5, Dec-26 
Sicilian Defense: Paulsen. Bastrikov Variation (B47)

1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 e6 3. d4 cd4 4. Nd4 Nc6 5. Nc3 Qc7 6. g4 a6 7. h4 b5 8. Nc6 dc6 9. Qf3 e5 10. g5 Be6 11. Bh3 Bh3 12. Rh3 Bc5 13. Bd2 O-O-O 14. O-O-O f6 15. h5 fg5 16. Bg5 Rd1 17. Nd1 Qd7 18. Qb3 Nf6 19. Rd3 Qg4 20. Be3 Be3 21. Ne3 Qe4 22. Qe6 Kb8 23. h6 Qh1 24. Rd1 Qh6 25. Qc6
